{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Warmup\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", "id": "msg_0196SUiSN9yx1buSAgnSCHkr", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I'm ready to help! I'm Claude Code, a file search specialist for Anthropic's CLI tool. \n\nI'm set up in the `/code` directory, which is a git repository on the `branch_1` branch. The repository is currently clean with no uncommitted changes.\n\nI can help you:\n- **Find files** using glob patterns to match filenames\n- **Search code** using regex patterns to find specific content\n- **Read files** when you know the exact path\n- **Explore the codebase** structure and organization\n\nJust let me know what you're looking for or what you'd like to explore in this codebase!"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 495, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 144, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
